title: Chris Brown`s daughter shows incredible dance moves at photo shoot
text: Chris Brown`s daughter shows incredible dance moves at photo shoot Wednesday, 14 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) *Washington D.C., Oct. 14(ANI): Chris Brown's daughter Royalty seems to be following her daddy's footsteps, especially, when it comes to getting down.* Washington D.C., Oct. 14(ANI): Chris Brown's daughter Royalty seems to be following her daddy's footsteps, especially, when it comes to getting down. The 26-year-old rapper was recently accompanied by his 17-month-old baby girl for a photo shoot for his upcoming album named on his daughter's name, reports E! Online. Brown posted a video on his Instagram , wherein his little one is seen showing some incredible dance moves while he stands behind her and smiles. Previously, the 'Loyal' hit-maker announced that he will be dropping his album on November 27.
